},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:46:54.000Z","msg":"沒事兒，沒事兒<br />\n<br />\n相信政府，身體健康，黨會赤手空拳戰勝肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5435df8c3add44ce9299ec85643b73b5c1fb2ae","tid":1843881,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6ddc136c2e63b5014ace74d4591b52a443494dc","tid":1843881,"uid":138609,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"05474571134fa99e749700524617cf90b3e62ddd","tid":1843881,"uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1b8c0e7a7a0e60d161115f9ed8946bf06930cae6","tid":1843881,"uid":313615,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>半年儲備</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"半年儲備for權貴"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"貿易戰要買2000億美國貨<br />\n今次有野買了<br />\n買清美國所有醫療裝備藥物<br />\n唔洗局住買大豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n農產品支那就點都要買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a2d39c1d8fdf02ab2fcff8eace5b02b797e6390","tid":1843881,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"我諗軍力都係咁<br />\n只能打14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a37f1b814b8abe1314795b9739c6c6c5bac34c","tid":1843881,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e708ca371e5d1e7e80a5d6062e756038b6ececd3","tid":1843881,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:27:53.000Z","msg":"工信部承認全國防護服生產力未能滿足湖北省需求<br />\n5分鐘前 Share to Facebook<br />\n【Now新聞台】在北京，國家衞生健康委員會表示，從臨床的經驗顯示，新型冠狀病毒傳播力有所增強，對防疫構成一定壓力，而工業及信息化部承認，全國防護服的生產力未能滿足湖北省的需求。<br />\n<br />\n內地新型冠狀病毒肺炎確診個案不斷上升，中央多個部委開記者會交代最新防疫措施。<br />\n<br />\n國家衞健委表示，春節假期是遏制武漢以外疫情蔓延的關鍵時期，是隔離、消毒措施發揮作用的最佳時間。<br />\n<br />\n他們承認，最新的臨床證據顯示，病毒人與人傳播力增強，對防疫構成一定的壓力。他們又考慮延長農曆新年假期。<br />\n<br />\n另外，陸續有捐贈物資，包括防護服、消毒液等，由全國各地送到湖北省， 統一發放到全省各地的醫療機構。<br />\n<br />\n不過，工業和信息部表示，根據湖北省的需求清單每天需要防護服十萬件，他們承認，全國的產能未能滿足武漢的需求。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，會使用中央儲備之外，亦正尋求在海外採購口罩、防護服等裝備。<br />\n<br />\n差不多所有出席記者會的人都戴口罩，國務院新聞辦公室 一改以往作風，沒有要求我們除下。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"大陸洗晒外匯買口罩，就係攬炒滅國的時候"},{"pid":"dde085662bfc0c605075dcb374ed0bcc1a2b4603","tid":1843881,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a2d39c1d8fdf02ab2fcff8eace5b02b797e6390","tid":1843881,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:47:57.000Z","msg":"我諗軍力都係咁<br />\n只能打14日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:48:30.000Z","msg":"根本支那呢個國家一黎料就見真章"},{"pid":"10bf86b36b7d13d43f8c894df06c4e3acbeee79f","tid":1843881,"uid":43041,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"呃鬼咩，十萬件一日都整唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n借d耳想外國捐比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce74335e9967c2113a1bb11d87cfc49898ad07f","tid":1843881,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b712ac5da3c1206679fae750f1d1622ce6101c","tid":1843881,"uid":37808,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"又話全球第2大經濟體 世界工廠 基建狂魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c22d726803b2e93fa33956967f8877a78bf81e63","tid":1843881,"uid":181649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dde085662bfc0c605075dcb374ed0bcc1a2b4